name: It was raining cats and dogs

metadata.name: Lay the dead girl
metadata.description:
Under the dim light, the girl quietly closed her eyes, her face was pale, her lips were white, and her rain-wet tangled hair clung to her delicate face.



Murong hongyi flashed, took a deep breath, and said quietly, "Get a knife and a bowl."



Murong, who had just finished speaking, was flanked by a dagger and a white porcelain bowl.



Murong Hong-yi, dagger and bowl in hand, stood over the corpse, staring at its pale, delicate face for a long time.
